>
>

# Test function definition
tokenize 'fn add($a, $b) { $a + $b }'
---
> Line 1:
>   [  0] Keyword(Fn)
>   [  1] Identifier("add")
>   [  2] Punctuation(OpenParen)
>   [  3] Variable("$a")
>   [  4] Punctuation(Comma)
>   [  5] Variable("$b")
>   [  6] Punctuation(CloseParen)
>   [  7] Punctuation(OpenCurly)
>   [  8] Variable("$a")
>   [  9] Operator(Plus)
>   [ 10] Variable("$b")
>   [ 11] Punctuation(CloseCurly)
>   [ 12] EOF
>
>

